## Deployment Tips
- For Vercel, ensure the `data/` folder is included in the repo or uploaded via GitHub Actions.
- Set `NEXT_PUBLIC_RENDER_BACKEND_URL` to your backend service URL.
- Use environment variables for sensitive data; do not commit them.

